RELIVE: The final World Cup press conference
You will soon be able to re-watch the final press conference of the 2014 FIFA World Cup Brazil™ which took place at the Maracana in Rio de Janeiro on Monday 14 July and was broadcast LIVE on 
. 
FIFA, the LOC and the Federal Government of Brazil were available to answer questions from the press and to provide a summary of the tournament. Participants speaking at the press conference included FIFA President Joseph S. Blatter, Brazil Minister of Sport Aldo Rebelo, LOC President Jose Maria Marin, Brazil Deputy Sports Minister Luis Fernandes, LOC Board of Administration member Ronaldo, LOC CEO Ricardo Trade and FIFA Secretary General Jérôme Valcke. 
